HudBumperStickerType.Name: One and Done
HudBumperStickerType.Label: OD
HudBumperStickerType.Description: C-bets at a high% on the flop, but then rarely double barrels.
HudBumperStickerType.ToolTip: One and Done | C-bets at a high% on the flop, but then rarely double barrels.

HudBumperStickerType.Name: Pre-Flop Reg
HudBumperStickerType.Label: PFR

HudBumperStickerType.ToolTip: Pre-Flop Reg | Plays an aggressive pre-flop game, but doesn’t play well post flop.

HudBumperStickerType.Name: Barrelling
HudBumperStickerType.Label: B

HudBumperStickerType.Name: 3 For Free
HudBumperStickerType.Label: 3FF
HudBumperStickerType.Description: 3-Bets too much, and folds to a 3-bet too often.

HudBumperStickerType.Name: Way Too Early

HudBumperStickerType.Name: Sticky Fish

HudBumperStickerType.Name: Yummy Fish
